Direct Known Subclasses:
CuramValueList, StringList
public class ValueList<E>
extends java.util.ArrayList<E>

Used as the superclass of "list" aggregations in value objects. Currently it provides the same functionality as java.util.ArrayList which means it is unsynchronized.
